            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "This will not work since b is a pointer so the c code has to be:\r\n```c\r\nTest* b = NULL;\r\nb->a += 1\r\n```\r\nor\r\n```c\r\nTest* b = NULL;\r\n(*b).a += 1\r\n```\r\nwhich is easier to generate. Current workaround is:\r\n```cython\r\ndereference(b).a = dereference(b).a  + 1\r\n```",
